Project notes
=============

- Run `python3 super_copilot_autofix.py` to validate/repair the marketplace scaffold.
- Run `python3 Jarvis_os/main.py` to start the full Jarvis OS stack.
- Tests: `pytest tests/ lovable_dev_test.py`
- Fintech JSON files live in golden_era_marketplace/fintech/.
- AI module stubs live in golden_era_marketplace/ai/<name>/<name>_ai.py.
